<subSubSection id="79BBA1EEBE5C39DB66369576888EB60E" pageId="null" pageNumber="227" type="description">
<paragraph id="E005B20AF78BBF6DB208C7429A6254F0" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<emphasis id="DED67DCB6CD763BC72A639C8EABCA848" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">P. rostrato-capitata</emphasis>
(Nr. 8) durch folgende Merkmale: Stengel, 
<normalizedToken id="BF0B6F1DF7928E6D04B9428748896958" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
(besonders die obern) und Blattstiele behaart; 
<emphasis id="F099254F4349A554062DE3757F5709DC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Kelch 7</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E587674C277576B68D95AFF1CDBC730E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">9 mm lang, dicht behaart</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="3FC634312535662467431F76D7DEE629" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Haare 1</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="F76B9C81058B77C4AA1E3840202BA77A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">2 mm lang</emphasis>
, mehrzellig); 
<emphasis id="A1DE7042E9C822676D8AC26A79A96D5C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Kronunterlippe kahl.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="ADF138ACDD3EE4AF88E0024D3866A4AC" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3C1066571C4EF61A0C444F1D1DF27C80" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">
<emphasis id="34E316F7D26C10D591E6B90320EF533B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="641D581705BE3D889DF6583D38258F54" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">
<emphasis id="A856566EC459BE8F02D2CD0342982654" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Steinige, lockere 
<normalizedToken id="BC277BB16C57B45CA642EE2EFF9314E8" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Grasige 
<normalizedToken id="B7DB17041537D8DF13B7A2ECCAB7D31B" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Haenge</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2E80CE70B650BC39FEF769FD79685FFB" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">
<emphasis id="B421C1F7A3424128399E1F404833D84E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Verbreitung. Westalpin-apenninische Pflanze:</emphasis>
Westalpen (Hautes Alpes, Savoyen und Piemont), 
<normalizedToken id="AE68FB365CA3B3D1A55526834005AC1B" originalValue="nördlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">noerdlicher</normalizedToken>
Apennin. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen (Tarentaise, Maurienne), 
<normalizedToken id="8C0C7EA2806FB9EF5BC440F6DC5A6F23" originalValue="Großer" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Grosser</normalizedToken>
St. Bernhard (
<normalizedToken id="E2B615DEDAE087849C7FF8A004A3F08F" originalValue="Südseite" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">Suedseite</normalizedToken>
), Grajische Alpen; nicht 
<normalizedToken id="7E42B4AD35B437921089BBAE9C99BE76" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="227">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
